Subject: [PATCH 04/16] Add support for dual boot

---
 Config.in          |   32 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 Makefile           |   18 +++++++++++++++---
 board/Config.in    |    4 ++++
 driver/MEDSdcard.c |   10 +++++++++-
 include/gpio.h     |    4 ++++
